collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (2 total Queries, 2 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `layout`.`jalur`, `layout`.`jumlah_box`, (layout.jumlah_box - COALESCE(SUM(stock.box_stock), 0)) AS space, SUM(COALESCE(stock.qty_stock, 0)) AS qty_stock, SUM(COALESCE(stock.box_stock, 0)) AS box_stock, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT tabel_induk.no_model SEPARATOR ', ') AS models, `layout`.`keterangan` FROM `layout` LEFT JOIN `stock` ON `layout`.`jalur` = `stock`.`jalur` LEFT JOIN `tabel_anak` ON `stock`.`id_anak` = `tabel_anak`.`id_anak` LEFT JOIN `tabel_induk` ON `tabel_induk`.`id_induk` = `tabel_anak`.`id_induk` GROUP BY `layout`.`jalur` ORDER BY `layout`.`jalur` ASC
